{"tid":593754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指「X」不吉利　要求九巴取消7、1、4　民建聯區議員：反映市民意見","createTime":"2018-03-15T09:08:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T11:04:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"202d12a2bef0c11af354ee35c534f2bc3757f7f6","tid":593754,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180315/s00001/987c5fc4c7e5ca3896a4220fe2981fcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180315%2Fs00001%2F987c5fc4c7e5ca3896a4220fe2981fcc.jpg&h=a367eb57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大埔公路上月10日發生九巴翻側奪命車禍，造成19人死亡，大埔區議會上周五（9日）開會討論事件。席間民建聯區議員黃碧嬌提到，「7」、「1」、「4」令人傷感，要求九巴勿用作車線號碼。言論引來網民嘲諷，黃碧嬌回覆《明報》時澄清，她是反映市民訴求。<br />\n<br />\n事緣黃碧嬌於會上表示，不少市民因是次意外，對雙層巴士產生恐懼，也非常抗拒新增路線872X，因「X」諧音是「去世」意思，又強烈要求勿用「7」、「1」、「4」號碼作巴士車線號碼，稱「好傷感」。<br />\n<br />\n其言論隨即被網民改圖廣傳，有網民直斥黃碧嬌荒謬、無腦，要求她示範如何把「X」讀成「去世」，又有網民質疑是否要取消英文字母「X」。另有網民表示，巴士路線號碼命名有既定規則，「唔係想幾多號就幾多號架」。<br />\n<br />\n至昨晚，黃碧嬌回覆《明報》時解畫，強調她是反映市民意見。黃碧嬌指，事發後聽到其 中一名死者同業、即的士司機意見，稱「點解要用返872？仲要加個X？毋須要重蹈覆轍，用返呢個咁大意外Number（號碼）」；亦有馬迷街坊表示：「上返872？你未死過啊？大吉利是加個『X』。」<br />\n<br />\n黃碧嬌指，已向對方解釋「X」代表特快、點對點，但重申今次事件嚴重，牽涉逾百家庭過千人，「精神心靈受到好大影響」。她續說，「（會上提到的）其實不是我自己意見。我講嘅都係我聽到佢哋聲音，我去代表佢哋表達，因為當時區議會唔可以咁長時間講咁多嘢啦」。<br />\n<br />\n黃碧嬌又認為，九巴須檢討收費標準，「每一個馬迷都問我，點解要收18.1元？1毫子你係咪真係收得咁多呢？點解唔係18元？點解要咁單丁？」她強調這並非「是否信邪」問題，而是「心靈安慰」，質疑「5公里（路程）收18.1元，你點解要咁做呢？你為乜嘢呢？」<br />\n<br />\n她引述九巴稱，對其建議持開放態度。<br />\n<br />\n另外，運輸署會上提到，會全面檢視有關路段道路環境及交通管理措施，如研究修訂車速限制、加強現有交通標誌、安裝固定偵測超速攝影機等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180315/s00001/1521103100572\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180315%2Fs00001%2F1521103100572&d=TJ3MZuC4%2BvlQOXGaWtZ5Af%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=b0122d5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180315%2Fs00001%2F1521103100572&h=f491fb57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180315/s00001/1521103100572</a>"},{"pid":"be0f7d01fcccf6856104b40007f737e9fa9436e4","tid":593754,"uid":74262,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a83dc8decafb119fbc3583fdfebb63774d3d27e6","tid":593754,"uid":60545,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"似去世？用支那話講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f6fca0ab042467990c2e08ef2a95b5571a01026","tid":593754,"uid":43839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be0f7d01fcccf6856104b40007f737e9fa9436e4","tid":593754,"uid":74262,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b787ebca0b9e85c2d6937bc4f0c890ada4a3d94","tid":593754,"uid":4661,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"7f6fca0ab042467990c2e08ef2a95b5571a01026","tid":593754,"uid":43839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be0f7d01fcccf6856104b40007f737e9fa9436e4","tid":593754,"uid":74262,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T09:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces